posting_body: ['Rare 2 Bedroom w/ Brand New Hardwood Floors Near the Water!!', 'Property Address', '512 5th Avenue West - #12-05 | Seattle, WA 98119', 'Available: Now', 'Offered By', 'Innovare-512 5th Ave W, LLC', 'Description', 'Located on a quiet street, surrounded by exceptional views of the Puget Sound and the Space Needle, The Standard is a residential solace within the city.', 'A place to enjoy charming and spacious homes, a place you can walk everywhere, a place your pet will love, a place to get to know your neighbors relaxing in the open-air courtyard or over a friendly game of outdoor ping pong.', '•Two bedroom home', '• Many windows with lots of light', '• Quartz counter-tops with tile back-splash', '• Hardwood flooring', '• Plenty of storage and closet space', '• On-site reserved parking', '• Laundry center', '• Community garden', 'In person and Facetime/ Zoom tours are available!', 'Contact us today to take your tour!', 'Amenities', 'Hard Surface', 'Flooring Throughout', 'Renovated Kitchen', 'Abundant Closet Space', 'Laundry Facility Onsite', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 2BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 700', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $2,195.00', 'Available: Now', 'Application Fee: $50.00', 'Security Deposit: $500.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs allowed']
